&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Praxis, we turn neuroscience discoveries into treatments to improve patients’ lives.&amp;nbsp; As our Monitoring Oversight Lead, you’ll play a key role in making sure our studies are conducted to the highest standards. You’ll develop and manage strategies that keep trial data accurate, compliant, and inspection-ready, while helping our sites and partners perform at their best.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications and Key Success Factors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
