&lt;li&gt;Review monitoring reports, assess site and CRA performance, and identify trends or issues early.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Clinical Operations, Data Sciences, QA, and CRO partners, if applicable, to drive excellence in trial execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform risk assessments and develop proactive strategies for issue detection and prevention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare clear, actionable monitoring oversight reports and CAPA plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support ongoing training and mentoring of CRAs, oversight staff, and vendor teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure inspection and audit readiness for all monitoring activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The physical and mental requirements of our roles include but are not limited to regular use of a computer, devices or other office equipment, clear communication, and occasional movement.&amp;nbsp; You&#39;ll need comfort with screen work, basic hand coordination, and focus. &amp;nbsp;Reasonable accommodations may be made to enable individuals with disabilities to perform these functions.&lt;/li&gt;
