&lt;li&gt;Internally and externally communicate a shared and bold vision for the program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, manage, and maintain the Program Team, partnering with functional leads to ensure team effectiveness and operational excellence while retaining clear accountability for program-level decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the creation and execution of the program strategy and integrated development plan(s).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In collaboration with the Program Team, define and deliver against program OKRs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic oversight for program budgets and resourcing, actively shaping—not just tracking—investment decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect scenarios to inform decision making and program planning; ensure that the right skills and capabilities exist on the team to effectively execute on the program plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a role model for Praxons: inspire ambitious goals, give and receive direct feedback, and build trust through transparency and follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;“Roll up sleeves and get hands dirty” for the benefit of the team and the program; wear multiple hats, step into gaps, and hold yourself to the same standards as the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary integration point with corporate processes without creating unnecessary bureaucracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
